		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">Shiru wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">I recall tried to use it, but in the emulator I was used for testing it was looking the same as one step lower brightness, so it didn't added any extra steps.</div>
<br />It should add one extra step, if setting all of the tint bits at once, or 3 steps if setting them one at a time. The idea was to set the tint bits as the very first thing in the fade, then after that just fade out normally.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
