		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It is definitely smooth, and additonal steps from the emphasis bits add extra smoothness. I would prefer 'subtract $10' version, though, because the RGB fade distorts colors, adds some greenish shade to them, albeit it looks smoother.

		

		</td>
